short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save, delete, and manage tabs in Google Chrome.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
TabManager is a Google Chrome extension that helps you efficiently manage your open tabs by providing a variety of useful options. With TabManager, you can view all your open tabs listed in a single window, making it easy to navigate and switch between them.

In addition to this, TabManager allows you to save open tabs for later use. You can save individual tabs or save an entire window's worth of tabs as a single session. This feature is especially handy when you want to continue working on a specific task or project later on.

When you no longer need the saved tabs, you can delete them individually or all at once with just a few clicks. Similarly, you can close open tabs individually or all at once to free up system resources and improve your browsing experience.

Overall, TabManager is a great tool for anyone who wants to stay organized and efficient while browsing the web. Whether you're a busy professional or a casual user, this extension can help you stay on top of your tabs and save time in the process.
